  "description": "For this wholesome, Omega 3 packed salad, you'll combine delicate mackerel with a vibrant quinoa, green bean and spinach salad. You'll dress the lot with a zesty lemon and caper dressing to make a totally tempting, satisfying bowl of goodness! (Gluten and dairy-free, suitable for coeliacs).",
